        public static SqlType applyResolved(ParamType schema,
                                    java.util.Map<GenericType,SqlType> resolved)
        Replaces all generics in a schema with concrete schemas defined in resolved
        Parameters:

      • reserveGenerics

        public static java.util.Map<GenericType,SqlType> reserveGenerics(ParamType schema,
                                                                 SqlArgument instance)
        Identifies a mapping from generic type to concrete type based on a schema and an instance, where the instance schema is expected to have no generic types and have the same nested structure as schema.
        Parameters:
        schema - the schema that may contain generics
        instance - a schema with the same structure as schema but with no generics
        Returns:
        a mapping from generic type to resolved type, an exception is thrown if the mapping failed

      • reserveGenerics

                                                                                        SqlArgument instance,
                                                                                        java.util.Map<GenericType,SqlType> reservedGenerics)
        Identifies a mapping from generic type to concrete type based on a schema and an instance, where the instance schema is expected to have no generic types and have the same nested structure as schema. Adds the mapping to an existing mapping passed into the function
        Parameters:
        schema - the schema that may contain generics
        instance - a schema with the same structure as schema but with no generics
        reservedGenerics - mapping of generic type to resolved type
        Returns:
        if the mapping succeeded and if it failed, an exception with why it failed
